title: Healthy Ep. 2 - Telling Your Story Could Change Everything with Jim Cofield
description:
This conversation made me cry because what Jim Cofield shares today might be the hardest thing you could do and yet could be the catalyst to real change. “What we don’t own about ourselves, will own us.” Join us.

Find Jim's ministry here: https://crosspointministry.com/
Jim's book here: https://www.amazon.com/Relational-Soul-Moving-False-Connection/dp/0830835873
